R

RelationClass - Class in org.relationlearn.util
Utility class used to represent the default class Attribute to be used in classifier training or instance classificaction.
RelationDigraph - Interface in org.relationlearn.model
The RelationDigraph interface represents a directed weighted graph used to store all arguments in the form of ArgumentNode objects and the relations between those nodes in the form of ArgumentRelation objects.
RelationImpl - Class in org.relationlearn.model
An ArgumentRelation implementation.
RelationImpl(int, ArgumentNode, ArgumentNode) - Constructor for class org.relationlearn.model.RelationImpl
Constructs a new RelationImpl with id rID, origin node aNd, destination node tNd and RelationType set to RelationType.UNKNOWN.
RelationImpl(int, ArgumentNode, ArgumentNode, RelationType) - Constructor for class org.relationlearn.model.RelationImpl
Constructs a new RelationImpl with id rID, origin node aNd, destination node tNd and RelationType rT.
RelationType - Enum in org.relationlearn.util
Enumerator used to describe the possible types of relation between two ArgumentNode objects in a RelationDigraph.
